17fca5a4-9362-4432-a309-f1a11dd32e9a.title: Captain Lawgof
17fca5a4-9362-4432-a309-f1a11dd32e9a.text:
Guthix be praised, the cavalry has arrived! Hero, how
would you like to be made an honorary member of the
Black Guard?

742d2023-993d-4d9f-9edc-6e61fe7bb64c.title: Captain Lawgof
742d2023-993d-4d9f-9edc-6e61fe7bb64c.text:
Hawhaw! 'What's that' she asks, what a sense of
humour! The Black Guard is the finest regiment in the
dwarven army. Only the best of the best are allowed to
join it and then they receive months of rigorous

ab657840-7401-41db-b4ae-b11f42de222d.title: Captain Lawgof
ab657840-7401-41db-b4ae-b11f42de222d.text:
training. However, we are currently in need of a hero,
so for a limited time only I'm offering you, a human, a
chance to join this prestigious regiment. What do you
say?

6feee06a-042e-4027-a49a-9348120992ad.title: <player>
6feee06a-042e-4027-a49a-9348120992ad.text: I'm sorry, I'm too busy mining.

5486dbda-07a8-4d38-8b07-1c6036ef8381.title: Captain Lawgof
5486dbda-07a8-4d38-8b07-1c6036ef8381.text:
Well best make the most of it while you can, if the
goblins over-run us they'll descend on the mines like a
plague of locusts!

9fe48ef0-bf16-4880-b5a1-aa828c08f803.title: <player>
9fe48ef0-bf16-4880-b5a1-aa828c08f803.text: Sure, I'd be honoured to join.

ceb6a869-1765-4dba-a343-567faf774cfa.title: Captain Lawgof
ceb6a869-1765-4dba-a343-567faf774cfa.text:
That's the spirit! Now trooper, we have no time to waste
- the goblins are attacking from the forests to the
South. There are so many of them, they are
overwhelming my men and breaking through our

9626e04b-55a0-43da-9410-5598382c8a4f.title: Captain Lawgof
9626e04b-55a0-43da-9410-5598382c8a4f.text:
perimeter defences; could you please try to fix the
stockade by replacing the broken rails with these new
ones?

55f2a39e-c568-42a5-9d22-3f9330a59dff.text: The Dwarf Captain gives you six railings.

085c817d-b5cd-4992-97d0-7ad2a8a8a349.title: Captain Lawgof
085c817d-b5cd-4992-97d0-7ad2a8a8a349.text: Report back to me once you've fixed the railings.

a8d9e944-9e52-46c3-8289-2f69285787a1.title: Captain Lawgof
a8d9e944-9e52-46c3-8289-2f69285787a1.text: Hello, trooper, how are you doing with those railings?

74063a18-e871-40bb-bacb-1bcd23fc6b7b.title: Captain Lawgof
74063a18-e871-40bb-bacb-1bcd23fc6b7b.text:
The goblins are still getting in, so there must still be
some broken railings.

d4785bb2-bf87-4d66-9eda-3e05bcea0f29.title: <player>
d4785bb2-bf87-4d66-9eda-3e05bcea0f29.text: Don't worry, I'll find them soon enough.

2f283c34-fdea-422c-9a13-8f0422276b8b.title: Captain Lawgof
2f283c34-fdea-422c-9a13-8f0422276b8b.text:
Well done, trooper! The goblins seem to have stopped
getting in. I think you've done the job!

08320732-9941-4e2a-9fb5-8ca016930bc5.title: <player>
08320732-9941-4e2a-9fb5-8ca016930bc5.text: Great, I'll be getting on then.

f5d9db79-a1d7-4f89-8ecd-3050bcc1853c.title: Captain Lawgof
f5d9db79-a1d7-4f89-8ecd-3050bcc1853c.text: What? I'll have you jailed for desertion!

bb5adc2d-fc35-4971-bf48-8bb503aa8fff.title: Captain Lawgof
bb5adc2d-fc35-4971-bf48-8bb503aa8fff.text:
Besides, I have another commission for you. Just
before the goblins over-ran us we lost contact with our
watch tower to the South, that's why the goblins
managed to catch us unawares. I'd like you to perform

6e6edc5a-03ea-49e5-b9df-a2645b1cf357.title: Captain Lawgof
6e6edc5a-03ea-49e5-b9df-a2645b1cf357.text:
a covert operation into enemy territory, to check up on
the guards we have stationed there.

3b610d00-16dd-4080-87d2-62a621a129ae.title: Captain Lawgof
3b610d00-16dd-4080-87d2-62a621a129ae.text: They should have reported in by now ...

f8903b4a-26c4-42c3-a2d6-e662ae437ebf.title: <player>
f8903b4a-26c4-42c3-a2d6-e662ae437ebf.text: Okay, I'll see what I can find out.

0bce2f23-c9e0-4f89-8935-28e6330e46f7.title: Captain Lawgof
0bce2f23-c9e0-4f89-8935-28e6330e46f7.text:
Excellent! I have two men there, the dwarf-in-charge is
called Gilob, find him and tell him that I'll send him a
relief guard just as soon as we mop up these remaining
goblins.

69e6483a-f20a-492a-aaef-513fcba1f2d8.title: Captain Lawgof
69e6483a-f20a-492a-aaef-513fcba1f2d8.text: Hello, any news from the watchman?

3a11eeee-edbd-4142-ada5-c1826c83af04.title: Captain Lawgof
3a11eeee-edbd-4142-ada5-c1826c83af04.text: Well, as quick as you can then.

8ac1e1bc-45aa-498d-98c4-048af60e93ca.title: <player>
8ac1e1bc-45aa-498d-98c4-048af60e93ca.text: I had better take these remains.

7089eb56-16a2-4b0e-b664-ca221789d314.title: Captain Lawgof
7089eb56-16a2-4b0e-b664-ca221789d314.text: Have you been to the watch tower yet?

02329c81-3cb8-4bc7-b3e8-86d91cafa222.title: <player>
02329c81-3cb8-4bc7-b3e8-86d91cafa222.text: Yes, I went up but there was no one there.

a1ebe0c3-048c-4af6-9a1c-02917ad19563.title: Captain Lawgof
a1ebe0c3-048c-4af6-9a1c-02917ad19563.text:
That's strange, Gilob would never leave his post... His
son was also with him, something doesn't smell right.
Can you return and look for clues?

8310fc03-f4ae-4b4c-a1fd-4551c281978f.title: <player>
8310fc03-f4ae-4b4c-a1fd-4551c281978f.text: Of course, I'll do what I can.

efe79ed9-f573-4d36-880d-257fec6c1528.title: <player>
efe79ed9-f573-4d36-880d-257fec6c1528.text:
I have some terrible news for you Captain, the goblins
over ran the tower, your guards fought well but were
overwhelmed.

4d9c7ad7-206c-47dd-bfb7-448154bd2704.text: You give the Dwarf Captain his subordinate's remains...

811ba893-4a6c-4bc1-888b-089d73ddf09b.title: Captain Lawgof
811ba893-4a6c-4bc1-888b-089d73ddf09b.text:
I can't believe it, Gilob was the finest lieutenant I had!
We'll give him a fitting funeral, but what of his
command? His son, Lollk, was with him. Did you find
his body too?

a7983dd1-3c45-42ea-b2f4-0378b8eb0046.title: <player>
a7983dd1-3c45-42ea-b2f4-0378b8eb0046.text:
No, there was only one body there, I searched pretty
well.

fb7c7242-38cc-4b79-b316-d39aba846bb6.title: Captain Lawgof
fb7c7242-38cc-4b79-b316-d39aba846bb6.text:
The goblins must have taken him. Please traveller, seek
out the goblins' hideout and return the lad to us. They
always attack from the South-east, so they must be
based down there.

b5c1f6cf-d478-4f2c-945a-db7033dce8eb.title: <player>
b5c1f6cf-d478-4f2c-945a-db7033dce8eb.text: Okay, I'll see if I can find their hideout.

2fc9a6cc-db07-416f-bf08-8952adb7d24b.title: Captain Lawgof
2fc9a6cc-db07-416f-bf08-8952adb7d24b.text: Trooper, have you managed to find the goblins' base?

ffe4bd2e-902b-4f98-a021-07ed2b265f0c.title: <player>
ffe4bd2e-902b-4f98-a021-07ed2b265f0c.text: Not yet I'm afraid, but I'll keep looking...

4ce81614-d993-49fc-ac2f-11f7117f9f96.title: Captain Lawgof
4ce81614-d993-49fc-ac2f-11f7117f9f96.text:
He has, and I thank you from the bottom of my heart
- without you he'd be a goblin barbecue!

b335f13d-a294-4ee2-b6ad-f0cb5abe0924.title: Captain Lawgof
b335f13d-a294-4ee2-b6ad-f0cb5abe0924.text: In that case could I ask one more favour of you...

e062be9b-e1ce-4317-9029-f1dba0c565c5.title: Captain Lawgof
e062be9b-e1ce-4317-9029-f1dba0c565c5.text:
When the goblins attacked us some of them managed to
slip past my guards and sabotage our cannon. I don't
have anybody who understands how it works, could you
have a look at it and see if you could get it working for

options.text: Okay, I'll see what I can do.
Sorry, I've done enough for today.

ffce09e5-d6cc-49c2-b904-0202c6b99ea0.title: <player>
ffce09e5-d6cc-49c2-b904-0202c6b99ea0.text: Sorry, I've done enough for today.

fe954fb8-ef7c-4e2b-8c6b-cdea99864674.title: Captain Lawgof
fe954fb8-ef7c-4e2b-8c6b-cdea99864674.text:
Fair enough, didn't think you'd be able to help anyway,
not much chance for a human to be able to fix it when
the best dwarven engineers have failed.

30ee3591-7eab-4e3e-884d-b854812e0df0.title: <player>
30ee3591-7eab-4e3e-884d-b854812e0df0.text: Okay, I'll see what I can do.

ae492993-b6e9-4863-b028-4204d44f8025.title: Captain Lawgof
ae492993-b6e9-4863-b028-4204d44f8025.text: Thank you, take this toolkit, you'll need it...

d637c8db-5486-4124-a0e7-9de46bf55318.title: Captain Lawgof
d637c8db-5486-4124-a0e7-9de46bf55318.text: Report back to me if you manage to fix it.

8bcbd84f-6f64-40e4-9fd7-014c5982e58a.title: Captain Lawgof
8bcbd84f-6f64-40e4-9fd7-014c5982e58a.text:
How are you doing in there, trooper? We've been
trying our best with that thing, but I just haven't got
the patience.

d4af161b-b387-4118-87ce-1c1e176c77f3.title: <player>
d4af161b-b387-4118-87ce-1c1e176c77f3.text: It's not an easy job, but I'm getting there.

b2686538-6f5c-47a3-a249-8c68db2adc08.title: Captain Lawgof
b2686538-6f5c-47a3-a249-8c68db2adc08.text:
Good stuff, let me know if you have any luck. If we
manage to get that thing working, those goblins will be
no trouble at all.

6447a4a2-64ee-4ab1-a9fe-8f5760fc21b6.title: <player>
6447a4a2-64ee-4ab1-a9fe-8f5760fc21b6.text: I'm afraid I lost the toolkit...

d26603db-29a7-4bd2-b4ee-16628e68366d.title: Captain Lawgof
d26603db-29a7-4bd2-b4ee-16628e68366d.text: That was silly... never mind, here you go.

c3d3fb97-0480-4d8a-aecb-476227278717.title: <player>
c3d3fb97-0480-4d8a-aecb-476227278717.text: Well, I think I've done it, take a look...

11c02b43-b562-405e-bd90-051726ab86bb.title: Captain Lawgof
11c02b43-b562-405e-bd90-051726ab86bb.text:
Well I don't believe it, it seems to be working perfectly!
I seem to have underestimated you, trooper!

0994f746-f3ce-4428-9da9-9e3b657fd43e.title: <player>
0994f746-f3ce-4428-9da9-9e3b657fd43e.text: Not bad for an adventurer eh?

a36ae557-6992-4a8d-823a-6c9e5b056cea.title: Captain Lawgof
a36ae557-6992-4a8d-823a-6c9e5b056cea.text:
Not bad at all, your effort is appreciated, my friend.
Now, if I could figure what the thing uses as ammo...

673fe32b-8b9b-441e-8e2a-b98fd887c59d.title: Captain Lawgof
673fe32b-8b9b-441e-8e2a-b98fd887c59d.text:
The Black Guard forgot to send instructions. I know I
said that was the last favour, but...

8a9036a7-db7a-42c4-af25-95aa515f59e0.title: Captain Lawgof
8a9036a7-db7a-42c4-af25-95aa515f59e0.text:
I can't leave this post, could you go to the Black Guard
base and find out what this thing actually shoots?

e92f49d8-eb16-44fc-bce3-bbd8a4694766.title: Captain Lawgof
e92f49d8-eb16-44fc-bce3-bbd8a4694766.text:
That's great, we were lucky you came along when you
did. The base is located just South of the Ice Mountain.

7d86a320-9a0a-42fa-a1dd-3794592fa229.title: Captain Lawgof
7d86a320-9a0a-42fa-a1dd-3794592fa229.text:
You'll need to speak to Nulodion, the Dwarf Cannon
engineer. He's the Weapons Development Chief for the
Black Guard, so if anyone knows how to fire this thing,
it'll be him.

08dd37a9-c001-4732-81bb-e70c81c66d74.title: <player>
08dd37a9-c001-4732-81bb-e70c81c66d74.text: Okay, I'll see what I can do.

a4e4bbf6-46ba-481d-9e20-15c3abcb39b7.title: MISSING
a4e4bbf6-46ba-481d-9e20-15c3abcb39b7.text: There is a message sent in chat here

6e834c4a-ac30-497c-b231-d995458bfad6.title: Captain Lawgof
6e834c4a-ac30-497c-b231-d995458bfad6.text: Hello trooper, any word from the Cannon Engineer?

6b718fd7-8fbf-4a02-9bfc-4fa65a64cd27.title: Captain Lawgof
6b718fd7-8fbf-4a02-9bfc-4fa65a64cd27.text:
The Black Guard camp is South of the Ice Mountain,
the quicker we can get some ammo for this thing the
quicker those Goblins will leave us be.

6c452696-ec46-4e07-b271-c840f43eea85.title: Captain Lawgof
6c452696-ec46-4e07-b271-c840f43eea85.text: Hello trooper, any word from the Cannon Engineer?

8a96bf0b-af27-46af-8044-f085f933c4e0.title: <player>
8a96bf0b-af27-46af-8044-f085f933c4e0.text: Yes, I have spoken to him.

d1950f1a-6a3f-490a-b678-14425b9ad1db.title: <player>
d1950f1a-6a3f-490a-b678-14425b9ad1db.text:
He gave me some items to give you... but I seem to
have lost something.

d621c3a4-51e1-48c3-9e64-8e825a445ff0.title: Captain Lawgof
d621c3a4-51e1-48c3-9e64-8e825a445ff0.text: If you could go back and get another, I'd appreciate it.

3628de60-e725-4d5b-8ffd-beee2fd17bb2.title: <player>
3628de60-e725-4d5b-8ffd-beee2fd17bb2.text:
He gave me an ammo mould and some notes to give to
you...

b62e95cc-4509-4eae-b613-7fb2a176b7cc.title: Captain Lawgof
b62e95cc-4509-4eae-b613-7fb2a176b7cc.text:
Aah, of course, we make the ammo! This is great, now
we will be able to defend ourselves. I don't know how to
thank you...

925e533a-e208-4ff6-83f6-b4dd80ac8ec5.title: <player>
925e533a-e208-4ff6-83f6-b4dd80ac8ec5.text: You could give me a cannon...

cca0e611-8dfb-4c22-90f4-3c65c8213891.title: Captain Lawgof
cca0e611-8dfb-4c22-90f4-3c65c8213891.text: Hah! You'd be lucky, those things are worth a fortune.

39b0e301-106b-4659-88ec-33563d8556ef.title: Captain Lawgof
39b0e301-106b-4659-88ec-33563d8556ef.text:
I'll tell you what though, I'll write to the Cannon
Engineer requesting him to sell you one. He controls
production of the cannons.

125874b6-a1b1-4cd9-993b-91196e4b64bc.title: Captain Lawgof
125874b6-a1b1-4cd9-993b-91196e4b64bc.text:
He won't be able to give you one, but for the right
price, I'm sure he'll sell one to you.

d0913d76-0158-4931-b10a-3efec284981a.title: <player>
d0913d76-0158-4931-b10a-3efec284981a.text:
Hmmm... sounds interesting, I might take you up on
that.

efff09ba-bfba-42e6-b5f5-fc33fde7679d.title: Captain Lawgof
efff09ba-bfba-42e6-b5f5-fc33fde7679d.text: Well hello there, how you doing?

35992ce1-db35-4c52-a9e5-5059b46438f1.title: Captain Lawgof
35992ce1-db35-4c52-a9e5-5059b46438f1.text:
I'm great now, those goblins can't get close with this
cannon blasting at them!
